prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant comic book cover featuring two main characters, Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo, reimagined as comic book heroes. The setting is a dynamic, sun-drenched beach with stylized waves crashing in the background. In the foreground, Jordan is illustrated mid-air, leaping heroically with a huge smile, holding a giant, comically oversized birthday bone with a ribbon on it. Lao Lao stands on the sand, laughing and striking a playful, triumphant pose with one hand on her hip, as if she just summoned her heroic partner. She wears the blue sweatshirt and black pants from the photo. Jordan wears the brown hoodie and dark pants from the photo. The scene is filled with classic comic book elements: a bright yellow sunburst behind the characters, dynamic action lines, and a bold, black outline style. Halftone dot patterns are used for shading, adding to the vintage comic aesthetic. Centered in the middle of the composition, the text is written in a beautiful, flowing handwritten cursive script inside a white, jagged-edged speech bubble.

Text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"
